These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
City: hamburg, venice, london, edinburgh
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, daisy, begonia
1. the person traveling to london is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsorchid##2
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
3. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
4. the person who growsorchid is not the person traveling to london##6
5. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | edinburgh  | hamburg | london | venice  |
| Flower   | iris | daisy   | begonia  | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, bus, scooter, roller
City: boston, nizza, miami, liverpool
1. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
3. the person driving the van is the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the van and the person driving the bus##2
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person traveling to boston##7
6. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
7. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Transport   | scooter | bus          | roller | van     |
| City    | miami      | liverpool | boston | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, bridge, monopoly
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, coral, aquamarine
1. the person who likes lavender is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
2. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
7. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game           | backgammon | whist | bridge     | monopoly |
| Color   | purple    | aquamarine   | lavender | coral    |

