.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, daisy, sunflower
City: nizza, marseilles, miami, hamburg
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growssunflower is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8
5. the person who growsiris is the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Flower   | daisy   | marigold         | sunflower   | iris    |
| City         | marseilles | hamburg | miami | nizza |

