.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, october, march
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, board-games, video-games
1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in november##7
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in april##7
4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's hobby is chess##7
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
7. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | november   | october | march | april    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | video-games   | board-games   | chess |

