.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
House: ranch-style, palace, farmhouse, colonial
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, cricket, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
6. the colonial house is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8
7. the colonial house is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| House          | colonial | ranch-style | palace  | farmhouse |
| Sport   | climbing   | water-polo         | cricket | snowboarding |

