.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, yellow, grey
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, van, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8
2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person driving the motorbike##7
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8
6. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Color   | lilac      | yellow | ivory | grey   |
| Transport      | trike | motorbike | jet-ski  | van |

