.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, drawing, hiking
House: wooden, townhouse, ranch-style, art-deco
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the wooden house##2
2. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
5. the townhouse house is the townhouse house##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the ranch-style house##6
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
8. the wooden house is not to the left of the townhouse house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | hiking   | baking | drawing | chess |
| House     | art-deco | townhouse       | wooden  | ranch-style    |

