.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-11::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, cat, goat
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, backgammon, billiard
1. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
4. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
5. the person playing domino is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Pet   | hamster     | goat | cat | pony |
| Game     | backgammon | billiard  | domino    | canasta   |

