2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City    | hannover        | berlin | hamburg      | marseilles    |
| Sport   | rowing | tennis   | skateboarding | cycling |

