.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, brown, ivory, emerald
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, architect, dressmaker, bartender
 1. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
 2. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
 3. the person who likes black is the dressmaker##1
 4. the dressmaker is not to the right of the architect##8
 5. the bartender is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 6. the architect is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 7. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes black is not to the right of the dressmaker##8
 9. the architect is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
10. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the musician##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Color          | brown    | ivory | black | emerald |
| Job   | musician | bartender  | dressmaker     | architect    |

