2. the fan of rock is not to the right of the fan of country##8
3. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of country##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
7. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | rock   | country    | techno   | blues |
| Birthday   | june | may | august | july |

