6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Color           | brown | lavender | green | blue   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure       | martial-arts      | satire    | fantasy |

