.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
House: cottage, wooden, craftsman, futuristic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not the cottage house##6
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the futuristic house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
4. the craftsman house is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the futuristic house is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in january##7
6. the futuristic house is on the left of the cottage house##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in july and the craftsman house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House         | wooden    | futuristic | cottage | craftsman |
| Birthday   | october | july      | november     | january     |

 